        {
            "title": "雲南潑水節｜車外人語音解鎖開車門射水？ 理想汽車澄清：須手動打開",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"車外人一句「理想同學打開車門」語音解鎖？ 理想汽車澄清：車門須手動打開\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/f82d1457d8e512ef835885783558f0d6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250418/_2025041817393074770.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">車外人一句「理想同學打開車門」語音解鎖？ 理想汽車澄清：車門須手動打開</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>近日，有一段「雲南潑水節理想汽車被潑成水浸」的視頻在網絡上傳開。有傳言稱，一輛理想汽車出現在雲南潑水節現場，副駕拿著水槍在車內躲避外面的攻擊。結果車外有人喊話「理想同學，打開車門」，導致解鎖了車門。外面的遊客拉開趁車門開了，向車內人員瘋狂潑水。事後，車主表示車輛因進水發生損壞。\n\n</p><h2>理想汽車：不支持語音解鎖</h2>\n<p>網絡熱傳視頻顯示，一輛黑色理想汽車在雲南潑水節現場被圍堵，有人在車外喊「理想同學，打開車門」，隨後副駕駛位的車門打開，眾人往車內潑水。相關視頻引發熱議後，有網友指出「誰都能開門，那要鎖幹啥」，「『理想同學』可以被車外人利用語音開門的嗎」。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網傳影片，有人叫出一句「理想同學，打開車門。」\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d37271da121a6b41f6286313aa844e0c/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h16m50s034.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網傳影片，有人叫出一句「理想同學，打開車門。」\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"網傳影片，雲南潑水節車內人和車外人在對峙。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/96aee59ab389e6c9b0c2087366663346/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h16m59s822.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網傳影片，雲南潑水節車內人和車外人在對峙。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f9425c737e49951b8355e0289f37d96f/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h17m11s023.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2645f7839c12f3091fb3205d51ed8379/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h17m18s443.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f2a486932f44bb32b4c2a1bf179506f3/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h17m24s167.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3a39d5bf81ee2057c127dbfa0f377cce/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h17m28s961.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1ae95a09fa18ea99a822966977c31f36/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h17m33s256.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb789f650c2dee3c3d99f2917a291f0e/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h17m40s622.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1a055f0cbba13af75adcc448cd8ed0ec/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h17m48s041.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        車門打開後，車內男子被瘋狂射水。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"理想汽車副總裁劉傑發視頻證副駕駛位的乘客自己手動打開車門。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a8c76427659cfccc6e1014e3177a489c/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h18m09s628.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        理想汽車副總裁劉傑發視頻證副駕駛位的乘客自己手動打開車門。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"理想汽車找來產品經理幫忙做了個測試，不支持車內車外語音解鎖。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/83ba3da77fbf555df3104e5f627bdd65/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h18m30s843.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        理想汽車找來產品經理幫忙做了個測試，不支持車內車外語音解鎖。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"理想汽車找來產品經理幫忙做了個測試，不支持車內車外語音解鎖。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/3c61c82b90cbb211f33a4e1f70f0717f/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h18m44s537.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        理想汽車找來產品經理幫忙做了個測試，不支持車內車外語音解鎖。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"理想汽車找來產品經理幫忙做了個測試，不支持車內車外語音解鎖。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5279e1b061e487067df2527f6e51d826/2025-04/vlcsnap-2025-04-18-17h25m41s415.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        理想汽車找來產品經理幫忙做了個測試，不支持車內車外語音解鎖。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3332622/\">雲南潑水節公告 嚴禁借機調戲婦女</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>相關話題近日登上熱搜，引發公眾對「理想同學」可被車外人利用的擔憂。4月17日晚，理想汽車副總裁劉傑對此回應稱，事實上，通過網上完整的視頻可以看出，是副駕駛位的乘客自己手動打開車門，理想汽車不支持通過車機語音解鎖車輛，更不支持通過車外語音喚醒打開車門。他還表示，自己也找來產品經理幫忙做了個測試。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2064646/即時-中國-雲南潑水節-車外人語音解鎖開車門射水-理想汽車澄清-須手動打開",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-18 17:56:03",
